parameters: Mage-like Man: Is this all for this month?

Dealer: Yes. I believe this is a sufficient amount. If you
ask for more, all our little rats down there will be wiped
out.

Mage-like Man: It's not for you to decide what's sufficient.
Just make sure you prepare what's been ordered as per the
request.

Mage-like Man: You're aware of the current situation, aren't
you? In addition to the usual required amount, there's the
production of weapons. The site needs a lot more magic ore
crystals. Much more.

Mage-like Man: And yet, it seems that the samples for this
experiment from your side are few. What's the meaning of
this?

Dealer: Well, recently there seems to have been a bit of a
coup in the mines, and we're in quite a bind here. So, could
you possibly give us a break just for this month?

Mage-like Man: Tch. I've told you to manage things properly.
How much do you think we're paying you? I hope no
information has leaked out. Remember, your payment includes
a fee for your silence.

Dealer: I understand. From now on, we'll impose stricter
rules and take care of the management guys to tighten up the
system...

Mage-like Man: Well, fine. The regular transactions will
continue as usual, near the royal capital... that's fine,
right...
Dealer: Of course. Then... on the... day of... month...

(This is troublesome. Are they being cautious, lowering
their voices like that? I'd rather not resort to force, but
should I barge into the room...?)

(However, if there were preparations for magical weapons
like earlier, it would cause significant damage to the
establishment. If either side learns of our intentions and
we let them slip away, it would all be for naught.)

(Should I let one side go and focus on the dealer who would
be easier to catch? Hmm, what to do...)

Half-naked Male Customer: Huh? You're already in the room?
You're an eager one, aren't you? ♪
(Damn it! Have I been spotted by their accomplices?!)

Half-naked Male Customer: But but, I like a proactive girl.
Do you like naughty things that much? Then let me sit next
to you.
Erm... so, I mean, that is...

(I panicked for a moment, but it seems he's just a regular
customer of this establishment. But still, just when I'm so
close! Damn it! Don't interfere now...!)

Half-naked Male Customer: Hm? Hey, aren't you different from
the girl I chose at the reception? Your face isn't the same,
is it?

Half-naked Male Customer: What should I do? In cases like
this... should I call someone from the shop? But I want to
enjoy my time fully while I'm here.

(Gah... The manager is aware of the situation, but my
current actions are my own decision... If I call someone
from the shop now and cause a scene, I'll definitely be back
to square one!)

Dear Guest♪ That's not true at all? You did choose me
properly...♪

(Anyway, I can't leave this place now. I have to bluff my
way through this!!)

Half-naked Male Customer: Is that so? It was dim and if you
ask me if I really saw your face clearly, it's doubtful.

Half-naked Male Customer: But well, even if you're not the
same person, with such a cute girl like you, gufu,
gufufufufufu♪

(Don't get so close! Don't touch me! Ugh... This guy must
have drunk quite a bit; he reeks of alcohol!)

Half-naked Male Customer: You're a face I don't see around
here much. What about it? Did you just start working here
recently?

Ah, yes, that's right. So I'm not quite used to the job
yet... It would help if you could overlook my shortcomings.

Half-naked Male Customer: That's tough. You've got a good
figure though; firm where it needs to be. Did they send you
out here from a rural area to earn some money?

Half-naked Male Customer: Ever since the change of rulers in
the royal capital, taxes have become harsher and life has
gotten tougher on top of military expansion. Do those castle
folks have no human heart at all...
Well... more or less as you've guessed...

Half-naked Male Customer: You're such a brave girl. But you
know, when I hear such stories, it makes me even more
irresistible...!

Half-naked Male Customer: Ahh, no more holding back. My
balls are getting hot. I'm going to spoil you plenty today.
Now turn your butt this way and beg for it♪
